### Prompt Used on _NAME OF AI TOOL_

```In javascript, how can I display the html element from javascript, can you give me an example. I want to display the list of item when user click on the button.
Copy and paste the prompt used

```

The code prompt above was used [NAME](link) to generate the code shown below:

```
Copy and paste the entirety of the code generated by the AI Tool listed above.

```// 1. Our data
const fruits = ['Apple', 'Banana', 'Cherry', 'Dragonfruit'];

// 2. Select the elements
const button = document.getElementById('load-list');
const listContainer = document.getElementById('item-list');

// 3. Define the action
button.addEventListener('click', () => {
  // Clear the list first
  listContainer.innerHTML = '';

  // Loop through the data
  fruits.forEach(item => {
    // Create a new <li> element
    const li = document.createElement('li');
    
    // Set the text
    li.textContent = item;
    
    // Add it to the <ul>
    listContainer.appendChild(li);
  });
});

